\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Billings Translation Guide.\

\b0\fs24 Last updated: March 15th, 2009.\
\
This short document explains how to translate Billings into a different language. There are 3 steps.\
\

\b\fs28 1. Translate the interface\

\b0\fs24 This is probably the most important part of the translation process. You will find a folder called "FILES". This folder contains a bunch of .mcloc files. Open these files in the LocTouch application (also included, Leopard only), select your language and start the translation process. Remember to save frequently.\
There are many files, but the works can be done pretty quickly.\
\
