\b\fs28 2. Translate the reports and invoice templates\

\b0\fs24 Another important part is to translate the reports/invoice/estimate/statement templates. This requires a separate set of instructions. Contact AJ (see below) when you are ready to start this part.\
\

\b\fs28 3. Send to Marketcircle \

\b0\fs24 You can send in your translated files to AJ and ask for a build with your changes included. This can take a couple days.\
Send email to aj@marketcircle.com with example subject: French Billings Translations\
\
\

\b\fs28 Working with Others\

\b0\fs24 Use the forums to coordinate with others (if there are others that are working on translating to the same language) as to which files you should work on.\
\
\

